"title": "2590: Jesus Christ, triumphal entry of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "2590",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Jesus Christ rode into Jerusalem on a colt, royally yet humbly, to the rejoicing of his followers, but provoking opposition from the Jewish religious leaders.</p>\n<h2>The colt used in Jesus Christ's entry into Jerusalem</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's instructions to his disciples</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:29-Luke19:31\">LUK 19:29–19:31</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:1-Matt21:3\">MAT 21:1–21:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:1-Mark11:3\">MRK 11:1–11:3</a></p>\n<h3>The obedience of the disciples</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:6\">MAT 21:6</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:4-Mark11:6\">MRK 11:4–11:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:32-Luke19:34\">LUK 19:32–19:34</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's entry into Jerusalem</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:14-John12:15\">JHN 12:14–12:15</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:4-Matt21:5\">MAT 21:4–21:5</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:11\">ISA 62:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:9\">ZEC 9:9</a></p>\n<h2>The response of the crowd to Jesus Christ's entry into Jerusalem</h2>\n<h3>Proclamation of Jesus Christ's kingship</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:8\">MAT 21:8</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:8\">MRK 11:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:36\">LUK 19:36</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs9:13\">2KI 9:13</a> <em>Spreading cloaks on the road was an act of royal homage.</em></p>\n<h3>Proclamation of Jesus' messiahship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:9\">MAT 21:9</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:9-Mark11:10\">MRK 11:9–11:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:37-Luke19:38\">LUK 19:37–19:38</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:26\">PSA 118:26</a></p>\n<h3>Proclamation of Jesus Christ's victory</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:13\">JHN 12:13</a></strong> <em>Palm branches were used in celebration of victory.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:40\">LEV 23:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:27\">PSA 118:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:9\">REV 7:9</a></p>\n<h2>The response of the Pharisees to Jesus Christ's entry into Jerusalem</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:39-Luke19:40\">LUK 19:39–19:40</a></p>",
